column2: SELECT   s.specobjid, s.bestobjid, s.firstrelease, s.survey, s.sourcetype, s.class,   gal.ra, gal.raErr, gal.dec, gal.decErr, s.z, s.zErr, s.zwarning,    gal.r, gal.i, gal.g, gal.dered_r, gal.dered_i, gal.dered_g, gal.psfMag_g,   gal.petroMag_r, gal.extinction_r, gal.petroR5#_r INTO mydb.GALAXY_RED_galaxy FROM specobj as s   JOIN Galaxy as gal on gal.objid = s.bestobjid  WHERE    (primtarget & dbo.fPrimTarget(&&&) > #)
